==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Aubaine
<hw>Au`baine"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>aubain</ets> an alien, fr. L. <ets>alibi</ets> elsewhere.]</ety>
<def>Succession to the goods of a stranger not naturalized.</def>
<rj><au>Littr⟦eacute⟧.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Droit d'aubaine</b></col> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <cd>the right,
formerly possessed by the king of France, to all the personal property
of which an alien died possessed. It was abolished in 1819.</cd>
<rj><au>Bouvier.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Aube</ent>⟦br⟧
